 * get_new_mid(mid =abslot([i + j] / 2))
 * value > arr[mid]{
 *	i = mid + 1
 *	get_new_mid()
 * }
 *
 * value < arr[mid]{
 *	j = mid -1
 * 	get_new_mid()
 * }
 * value ==  mid return;
